rows.label: qev075202_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh. Apologies, warrior. I was lost in thought.
Shocking, I know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0003
rows.name:
I was just struck by how beautiful this forest is.
It reminds me of the land where I was whelped.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that you didn't come here to chat.

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0004
rows.name: I appreciate you showing an interest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0005
rows.name:
I can fill you in as we goâ€”woodland combat is bound
to take us a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0006
rows.name:
Ah ha ha! Oh, I like your style, my friend.
But I'm sure that fighting in the woods like this
will take us a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0007
rows.name:
Perhaps we can chat a bit as we go.
I would like to tell you something of my past.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075202_MSG0008
rows.name:
Now let us commence this fight, my friend.
Good luck spotting me out here![ST:wait ]
